# ☕ Coffee Shop Sales Analytics Dashboard

## 📌 Project Description

This project analyzes **coffee shop sales data** to understand daily operations, customer preferences, revenue patterns, and product performance in a busy café environment.

The dashboard tracks **orders, transaction values, popular items, hourly rush periods, payment methods, and profit margins** using interactive visuals built in **Power BI / Tableau / Python**.

> **Perfect for:** Café owners, restaurant managers, retail analysts studying F&B (Food & Beverage) sector.

