## 🎯 Key Business Questions Answered

| Question | Visual Solution |
|----------|----------------|
| Which drink sells the most? | Bar chart by product category |
| What are peak hours? | Heatmap or line chart (Hour vs Day) |
| Which location/branch performs best? | Map or comparative cards |
| Do members spend more than walk-ins? | Grouped bar or donut comparison |
| How does weather affect sales? | Scatter plot with trend line |
| What's our average basket size? | KPI card + breakdown |

---

## 📊 Core Metrics Tracked

<div align="center">

| Metric | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| **☕ Total Transactions** | Number of orders/bills generated |
| **💵 Gross Revenue** | Total sales before tax/discounts |
| **🥐 Avg Basket Size** | Items per order / Revenue per customer |
| **⭐ Customer Rating** | Average review score (1-5 stars) |
| **🔄 Repeat Rate** | % of returning customers |
| **🕒 Service Time** | Average minutes per transaction |
| **📦 Inventory Turnover** | Stock movement analysis |
| **📍 Branch Comparison** | Multi-location performance |

